{"id":54,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":54,"title":"Chapter 50: The Jaredites Leave Babel","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 50","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 50"],["h1","The Jaredites Leave Babel"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p3"},"Jared and his brother were righteous men who lived in a city called Babel. They lived hundreds of years before the Nephites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/1.33"},"Ether 1:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/11.9"},"Genesis 11:9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p5"},"Most of the people in Babel were wicked. They built a tower to try to get to heaven. The Lord became angry and changed their language."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/11.4,7"},"Genesis 11:4, 7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p7"},"Jared asked his brother to pray and ask the Lord not to change the language of their families and friends."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/1.34"},"Ether 1:34"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p9"},"The brother of Jared prayed, and the Lord answered his prayer. Jared, his brother, and their families and friends could still understand one another."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/1.35-37"},"Ether 1:35–37"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p11"},"The Lord told the brother of Jared to gather his family and friends and leave the land. They took their animals and all kinds of seeds with them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/1.41-42"},"Ether 1:41–42"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p13"},"The Lord said he would lead the Jaredites to a promised land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/1.42"},"Ether 1:42"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p15"},"The Jaredites caught birds and fish to take with them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.2"},"Ether 2:2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p17"},"They took swarms of honeybees."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.3"},"Ether 2:3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p19"},"The Jaredites traveled to the wilderness. The Lord spoke to them from a cloud and told them which way to go."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.5"},"Ether 2:5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p21"},"The Lord said the people who live in the promised land must serve God or they will be destroyed."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.7-8"},"Ether 2:7–8"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_054_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p23"},"When the Jaredites got to the seashore, they put up their tents. They stayed by the sea for four years."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-50-the-jaredites-leave-babel.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.13"},"Ether 2:13"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
